Key Match Events: Hasan Ali took the first wicket as he dismissed Max O'Dowd
Colin Ackermann was also dismissed by spinner Iftikhar Ahmed
Bas de Leede bowled a wonderful spell to restrict Pakistan innings to 286 runs
Aryan Dutt provided the team a breakthrough as he dismissed Saud Shakeel
Bas de Leede took from there and dismissed Mohammad Rizwan, Iftikhar Ahmed, Shadab Khan and Hasan Ali to derail the Pakistan batting
Miscellaneous Highlights: Rain interrupted play, reducing the game to 20 overs per side
